summary:
First thing my 8 year old says to me as soon as she wakes up: 2 more days left for @taylorswift concert!
Me: you know, it might...
body:
First thing my 8 year old says to me as soon as she wakes up: 2 more days left for @taylorswift concert!

Me: you know, it might rain on us

Her: who cares! We’re still gonna see @taylorswift

Me: *proudly looks at her*

Her: wait, is it going to be cancelled????

Me: nope, they don’t cancel.

Her: yayyy. Poor @taylorswift she’s gonna get wet.

Thank you @taylorswift for being part of our early morning conversations ❤❤❤❤❤
